expressions.expression:
CASE
  WHEN "total_connections" IS NULL THEN NULL
  WHEN "total_connections" = 1 THEN '1xOne-meter Enclosure'
  WHEN "total_connections" = 2 THEN '2xOne-meter Enclosure'
  WHEN "total_connections" = 3 THEN '3xOne-meter Enclosure'
  WHEN "total_connections" = 4 THEN '1xFour-meter Enclosure'
  ELSE
    concat(
      to_string(floor("total_connections" / 4.0)), 'xFour-meter Enclosure', 
      CASE 
        WHEN "total_connections" % 4 = 0 THEN ''
        ELSE concat(' and ', to_string("total_connections" % 4), 'xOne-meter Enclosure')
      END
    )
END
expressions.name: CASE WHEN "total_connections" IS NULL THEN NULL WHEN "total_connections" = 1 THEN '1xOne-meter Enclosure' WHEN "total_connections" = 2 THEN '2xOne-meter Enclosure' WHEN "total_connections" = 3 THEN '3xOne-meter Enclosure' WHEN "total_connections" = 4 THEN '1xFour-meter Enclosure' ELSE concat( to_string(floor("total_connections" 4.0)), 'xFour-meter Enclosure', CASE WHEN "total_connections" % 4 = 0 THEN '' ELSE concat(' and ', to_string("total_connections" % 4), 'xOne-meter Enclosure') END ) END
